history.content: Hi there, I recently enrolled into EECS 127, but I had a concern. A few weeks back when I added 127 to my schedule, there was a W 10-11am discussion that worked perfectly and I added it to my schedule. It sat in my shopping cart all this time no problems. Today when I go to my shopping cart to enroll, I notice that that class was still in my shopping cart, but when I went through the actual enrollingn process but it didn't show up in the schedule maker anymore. Initially I thought that discussion was cancelled but I went to classes.berkeley.edu to check all possible discussions and there were the original 6 there but only 4 of them are showing up on calcentral for enrollment? Any help with this is greatly appreciated. Thanks!
history.subject: EECS 127 missing discussions on schedule planner
